3. Information Collection and Use
Personal Data:
While using our Service, we may ask you to provide certain personally
identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you (“Personal Data”). This may
include your name, player id, email address, Discord username, and other contact information.
Usage Data:
We may also collect information on how the Service is accessed and used (“UsageData”). This data may include information such as your device’s Internet Protocol (IP) address,
device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, and other diagnostic data.
Game Progress Data:
We may collect data related to your in-game progress, such as scores,
achievements, and other gameplay statistics.
Purchase and Advertisement Targeting Data:
We may collect data related to your purchases
and subscriptions, and advertisement targeting data.
The information that we request will be retained by us and used as described in this privacy policy.
